    "description": "For the perfect Lunar New Year celebration, this one's a cut above the rest. You'll snip fresh dough into chewy, noodle pieces then toss with meat-free chick'n, pak choi and a gochujang-maple sauce. Sweet, spicy and oh-so special.",
